ing: 1/4 cup low-fat creamy salad dressing (such as Miracle Whip LightÂ®)
salt and ground black pepper to taste
des: "A new twist on an old classic, using fresh vegetables from your garden."
ins: Place zucchini in a colander and let drain thoroughly, about 30 minutes. Toss with carrot in a large salad bowl; stir in creamy salad dressing and sugar. Chill the coleslaw for 1 hour to blend flavors, stir again, and season with salt and black pepper.
